<!-- §9 What is [Product]? -->
<h2>What Is Mouth Tape and Why Is It Trending?</h2>
<p>Mouth tape is a simple adhesive strip that keeps your lips sealed during sleep, forcing nasal breathing. Once a niche biohacking practice, it's now mainstream thanks to sleep science advocates like Dr. James Nestor who popularized nasal breathing as the foundation of sleep quality. Breazy strips are specifically formulated for sleep — medical-grade adhesive that holds all night but peels off painlessly in the morning.</p>

